			</div>


			<div class="btnOne" id="memPostBtn">
				<span class="material-symbols-outlined"> edit_note </span> <span>게시물
					관리</span>
			</div>


			<div class="btnOne" id="memCmtBtn">
				<span class="material-symbols-outlined"> comment </span> <span>댓글
